response: * Elliott Johnson (born 1975), American artist and designer

Elliott Johnson (born 1975) is an American artist and designer.  He was born in Irving, Texas and earned a BFA in painting and drawing from the University of North Texas (Denton, Texas) in 2001.Chris Worley Fine Art  He lives and works in Dallas, Texas.
